[ About ]
Bold, cinematic
pitches built to
win the room.
Andrew Hague is a treatment designer specialising in bold, cinematic pitches that span high-gloss pop music videos, luxury automotive, high-level VFX, premium beauty, and sleek lifestyle campaigns.

His work has shaped treatments for artists like Ariana Grande, Tate McRae, and Doja Cat, as well as global brands including Nike, Bose, and McDonald's.
